==Chinese==

===Etymology===
From Chinese [[笙]] (pinyin: shēng); character consists of upper part ("bamboo") and lower part ("born")

===Noun===
'''sheng'''

#A Chinese wind instrument.  It is a free-reed mouth organ consisting of 13 or more bamboo pipes of various lengths, which are fixed at their bases in a wind chest made from a dried gourd (or, more recently, wood or chrome-plated brass).

